{"tid":178220,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[出公海]連登有冇人行船？想搭船去美國","createTime":"2017-03-29T11:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T16:43:12.000Z","uid":16584,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0be4aad2cf02efb7a787e8a976f40f21ce22dae6","tid":178220,"uid":16584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的，聽講以前啲人比人賣豬仔去舊金山<br />\n所以我成日ff搭船可以去到幾遠<br />\n<br />\ngoogle完一輪，近既可以（好似係）<br />\n廈門-&gt;基隆／金門 <a href=\"http://www.cosco.url.tw/product.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosco.url.tw%2Fproduct.html&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=931fe353\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cosco.url.tw/product.html</a><br />\n上海-&gt;日本／韓國 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">但係我想去遠啲呀!</span></span><br />\n於是再google多輪<br />\n<br />\n1、中美之間就沒有輪船客運，只有中轉，需要15天到45天，主要是根據航線和停泊的口岸來決定。<br />\n2、如果由中國到美國西部，可選擇上海-橫濱，橫濱-火奴魯魯，火奴魯魯-洛杉磯（或西雅圖）路線。<br />\n<br />\n我大哥2014年3.22坐船從香港出發 4.8到達long beach反正他護照上蓋著不一樣的碼頭港口的戳，感覺很炫酷<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">是找一個同學弄到的票不是遊輪</span>說走就走價格是比飛機貴一截經歷很棒的講不完的故事十幾天沒有網沒有手機信號卻有不一樣的人生體驗可愛的船長廣袤的星空與海洋被自然深深的感動<br />\n<br />\n姐係只要識人行船就有辦法跟上船？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以帶我出公海<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606145b0655675032012de580063bef435e6eee3","tid":178220,"uid":16584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055799faae8454160a979f234c865f169f1fe720","tid":178220,"uid":16584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd10adb4fdb3b42a00fd99548fbd058066bebc2","tid":178220,"uid":16584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":